data.title: Artist Collection
data.meta_description: Miles Davis' jazz on vinyl. A record of revolutionary sound. Shop this legend!
data.text: The Bootleg Series is a collection of rare recordings by Miles Davis, offering insights into his live performances and studio sessions. Spanning various phases of his career, it highlights the evolution and innovation of Davis' jazz artistry. These recordings feature some of his most iconic collaborations with legendary musicians. Each volume showcases Davis' enduring influence on music and is now available as a deluxe lift-off box set.
